data.description: Welcome to this charming and adorable 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch home located in the heart of Old Brooklyn! This delightful property offers a prime location within minutes of locally owned businesses like 787 Market & a winery, allowing you to enjoy the vibrant community! With easy highway access & proximity to the Metroparks Zoo, this home offers both convenience & entertainment options. Step inside & discover a home that has been thoughtfully updated, including a brand new roof, fresh paint, new kitchen cabinets, flooring and appliances that stay! The modern upgrades blend seamlessly with the home's timeless character. An  abundance of storage space, ensures a clutter-free living environment. The partially finished basement provides recreational space, perfect for setting up a home gym or hosting gatherings. The basement also houses a convenient laundry area. Outside, enjoy the spacious yard complete with an above ground pool, providing the perfect oasis for relaxation and enjoyment during warmer months. The two-car garage and newer privacy fence provide practicality and peace of mind. Additional features include a new hot water tank, ensuring reliability and efficiency. With two full baths, one on the main floor and another in the basement, you'll have all the convenience you need. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming home yours and envision the wonderful memories you can create in this well-maintained and updated property.
